  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个完整的OAuth2认证流程图，涉及Web Client、Keycloak和Synapse Server三个参与者。Web Client是公网客户端，Synapse Server是后端服务，Keycloak作为授权服务器。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Web Client (Public)",
        "Keycloak",
        "Synapse Server",
        "Authorization Server"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，三个参与者。我想确认一下：Synapse Server和Web Client都需要先在Keycloak注册吗？它们的注册方式有区别吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Keycloak",
        "client_id",
        "client_secret",
        "public client"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，两者都要注册，但方式不同。Synapse Server用confidential client方式，需要client_id和client_secret；Web Client是public client，只需要client_id，没有secret。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Synapse Server",
        "Web Client (Public)",
        "client_id",
        "client_secret",
        "client_credentials",
        "Authorization Code flow"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画出初始设置部分，标注两个注册流程。接下来是认证流程，Web Client走Authorization Code流程对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Initial Setup",
        "Register with client_id & client_secret",
        "Register with client_id (public)"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "没错，Web Client用Authorization Code with PKCE。步骤是：先请求授权码，Keycloak重定向返回code，然后Web Client用code加client_id换token，拿到access token和refresh token。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Authorization Code Request",
        "Redirect with Auth Code",
        "Token Request (code + client_id)",
        "Access & Refresh Tokens",
        "PKCE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "Synapse Server这边呢？它作为后端服务，应该是用client_credentials直接拿token？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Synapse Server",
        "client_credentials",
        "Token Request",
        "Access Token"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，Server Authentication这部分，Synapse用client_credentials向Keycloak请求，直接获得access token。然后进入API通信阶段。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Server Authentication",
        "client_credentials",
        "Access Token"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "API通信我画出来了：Web Client带token请求Synapse，Synapse向Keycloak做token introspection验证，通过后返回API响应。还需要补充什么吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "API Communication",
        "API Request + Access Token",
        "Token Introspection",
        "Token Validation Response",
        "API Response"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "最后加上Token Refresh环节。Web Client的access token会过期，需要用refresh token向Keycloak请求新的access token和refresh token。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Token Refresh",
        "Refresh Token Request",
        "New Access & Refresh Tokens"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完成了。我在右侧加了三个注释说明：Keycloak作为授权服务器和身份提供商，Synapse使用confidential client credentials flow，Web Client使用Authorization Code flow with PKCE。这样整个流程就完整了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Note right of K",
        "Note right of S",
        "Note right of W",
        "Authorization Server",
        "Identity Provider",
        "confidential client credentials flow",
        "Authorization Code flow with PKCE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    }
  ],
